data.name: Adductor Brevis
data.origin: Front of the inferior pubic ramus just below the origin of the adductor longus
data.insertion: Lower 2/3 of the pectineal line of the femur and the upper half of the medial lip of the linea aspera

data.name: Adductor Longus
data.origin: Anterior pubis just below its crest
data.insertion: Middle 1/3 of the linea aspera

data.name: Adductor Magnus
data.origin: Edge of the en- tire pubic ramus and the ischium and ischial tuberosity
data.insertion: Whole length of the linea aspera, inner condyloid ridge, and adductor tubercle

data.name: Anconeus
data.origin: Posterior surface of the lateral condyle of the humerus
data.insertion: Posterior surface of the lateral olecranon process and proximal 1/4 of the ulna

data.name: Biceps Brachii Long Head
data.origin: Supraglenoid tubercle above the superior lip of the glenoid fossa
data.insertion: Tuberosity of the radius and bicipital aponeurosis (lacertus fibrosis)

data.name: Biceps Brachii Short Head
data.origin: Coracoid process of the scapula and upper lip of the glenoid fossa in conjunction with the proximal attachment of the coracobrachialis
data.insertion: Tuberosity of the radius and bicipital aponeurosis (lacertus fibrosis)

data.name: Biceps Brachii Long Head
data.origin: Supraglenoid tubercle above the superior lip of the glenoid fossa
data.insertion: Tuberosity of the radius and bicipital aponeurosis (lacertus fibrosis)

data.name: Biceps Brachii Short Head
data.origin: Coracoid process of the scapula and upper lip of the glenoid fossa in conjunction with the proximal attachment of the coracobrachialis
data.insertion: Tuberosity of the radius and bicipital aponeurosis (lacertus fibrosis)

data.name: Biceps Femoris
data.origin: Long head: ischial tuberosity. Short head: lower half of the linea aspera, and lateral condyloid ridge
data.insertion: Head of the fibula and lateral condyle of the tibia

data.name: Brachialis
data.origin: Distal half of the anterior shaft of the humerus
data.insertion: Coronoid process of the ulna

data.name: Brachio-Radialis
data.origin: Distal 2/3 of the lateral condyloid (supracondylar) rydge of the humerus
data.insertion: Lateral surface of the distal end of the radius and the styloid process

data.name: Deltoid Anterior Fibers
data.origin: Anterior lateral third of clavicle
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Deltoid Anterior Fibers
data.origin: Anterior lateral third of clavicle
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Deltoid Middle Fibers
data.origin: Lateral aspect of acromion
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Deltoid Posterior Fibers
data.origin: Inferior edge of spine of ulna
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Deltoid Middle Fibers
data.origin: Lateral aspect of acromion
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Deltoid Posterior Fibers
data.origin: Inferior edge of spine of ulna
data.insertion: Deltoid tuberosity on lateral humerus

data.name: Gluteus Maximus
data.origin: Posterior 1/4 of the crest of the ilium, posterior surface of the sacrum and coccyx near the ilium, and fascia of the lumbar area
data.insertion: Oblique ridge on the lateral surface of the greater trochanter and the iliotibial band of the fasciae latae

data.name: Gluteus Medius
data.origin: Lateral surface of the ilium just below the crest
data.insertion: Posterior and middle surfaces of the greater trochanter of the femur

data.name: Gluteus Minimus
data.origin: Lateral surface of the ilium just below the origin of the gluteus medius
data.insertion: Anterior surface of the greater trochanter of the femur

data.name: Gracilis
data.origin: Anteromedial edge of the descending ramus of the pubis
data.insertion: Anterior medial surface of the tibia below the condyle

data.name: Iliacus
data.origin: Inner surface of the ilium
data.insertion: Lesser trochanter of the femur and shaft just below
action: Transverse pelvic rotation contralaterally when ipsilateral femur is stabilized

data.name: Infra-spinatus
data.origin: Infraspinous fossa just below spine of scapula
data.insertion: Posteriorly on greater tubercle of humerus

data.name: Latissimus Dorse
data.origin: Posterior crest of ilium, back of sacrum and spinous processes of lumbar and lower six thoracic vertebrae, slips from lower three ribs
data.insertion: Medial side of intertubercular groove of humerus, just anterior to the insertion of the teres major

data.name: Pectineus
data.origin: Space 1 inch wide on the front of the pubis just above the crest
data.insertion: Rough line leading from the lesser trochanter down to the linea aspera

data.name: Pectoralis Major upper fibers
data.origin: Medial half of anterior surface of clavicle
data.insertion: Flat tendon 2-3 inches wide to lateral lip of intertubercular groove of humerus

data.name: Pectoralis Major lower fibers
data.origin: Anterior surface of costal cartilages of first six ribs, and adjoining portion of sternum
data.insertion: Flat tendon 2-3 inches wide to lateral lip of intertubercular groove of humerus

data.name: Pectoralis Major upper fibers
data.origin: Medial half of anterior surface of clavicle
data.insertion: Flat tendon 2-3 inches wide to lateral lip of intertubercular groove of humerus

data.name: Pectoralis Major lower fibers
data.origin: Anterior surface of costal cartilages of first six ribs, and adjoining portion of sternum
data.insertion: Flat tendon 2-3 inches wide to lateral lip of intertubercular groove of humerus

data.name: Pronator Quadratus
data.origin: Distal 1/4 of the anterior side of the ulna
data.insertion: Distal 1/4 of the anterior side of the radius

data.name: Pronator teres
data.origin: Distal part of the medial condyloid ridge of the humerus and medial side of the proximal ulna
data.insertion: Middle 1/3 of the lateral surface of the radius

data.name: Psoas major and minor
data.origin: Lower borders of the transverse processes (L1–L5), sides of the bodies of the last thoracic vertebra (T12), the lumbar vertebrae (L1–L5), intervertebral fibrocartilages, and base of the sacrum
data.insertion: Lesser trochanter of the femur and shaft just below psoas minor; pectineal line (of pubis) and iliopectineal eminence
action: Transverse pelvic rotation contralaterally when ipsilateral femur is stabilized
Lateral flexion of the lumbar spine

data.name: Rectus Femoris
data.origin: Anterior inferior iliac spine of the ilium and groove (poste- rior) above the acetabulum
data.insertion: Superior aspect of the patella and patella tendon to the tibial tuberosity

data.name: Sartorius
data.origin: Anterior superior iliac spine and notch just below the spine
data.insertion: Anterior medial surface of the tibia just below the condyle

data.name: Semimembranosus
data.origin: Ischial tuberosity
data.insertion: Posteromedial surface of the medial tibial condyle

data.name: Semitendinosus
data.origin: Ischial tuberosity
data.insertion: Upper anterior medial surface of the tibia just below the condyle

data.name: Sub-scapularis
data.origin: Entire anterior surface of subscapular fossa
data.insertion: Lesser tubercle of humerus

data.name: Supinator
data.origin: Lateral epicondyle of the humerus and the neighboring posterior part of the ulna
data.insertion: Lateral surface of the proximal radius just below the head

data.name: Supra-spinatus
data.origin: Medial 2/3 of supraspinous fossa
data.insertion: Superiorly on greater tubercle of humerus

data.name: Teres Major
data.origin: Posteriorly on inferior third of lateral border of scapula and just superior to the inferior angle
data.insertion: Medial lip of intertubercular groove of humerus, just posterior to the insertion of the latissimus dorsi

data.name: Teres Minor
data.origin: Posteriorly on upper and middle aspect of lateral border of scapula
data.insertion: Posteriorly on greater tubercle of humerus

data.name: Triceps Brachii Lateral Head
data.origin: Upper half of the posterior surface of the humerus
data.insertion: Olecranon process of the ulna

data.name: Triceps Brachii Long Head
data.origin: Infraglenoid tubercle below inferior lip of the glenoid fossa of the scapula
data.insertion: Olecranon process of the ulna

data.name: Triceps Brachii Medial Head
data.origin: Distal 2/3 of the posterior surface of the humerus
data.insertion: Olecranon process of the ulna
